1565
01:00:46,366 --> 01:00:47,826
This transforms one way.

1566
01:00:47,906 --> 01:00:49,046
This transforms the other way.

1567
01:00:49,046 --> 01:00:50,406
For example,

1568
01:00:50,406 --> 01:00:52,506
if this happened to be

1569
