1581
01:01:27,786 --> 01:01:32,446
upstairs and downstairs in the y coordinates,

1582
01:01:32,826 --> 01:01:36,766
it is equal to a bunch of dx's

1583
01:01:36,766 --> 01:01:40,706
times dy's and dy's times dx's of various kinds

1584
01:01:40,706 --> 01:01:44,726
times the corresponding tensor in the x coordinates.

1585
01:01:47,465 --> 01:01:49,646
If it's zero on one side,

1586
01:01:49,646 --> 01:01:51,366
it's zero on the other side.

1587
01:01:52,206 --> 01:01:54,506
So if a tensor is zero,

1588
01:01:54,506 --> 01:01:55,106
in other words,

1589
01:01:55,106 --> 01:01:57,946
a tensor being zero means all of its components,

1590
01:01:58,086 --> 01:02:00,766
if all of its components are zero,

1591
01:02:01,805 --> 01:02:05,246
then it follows they are zero in every coordinate system.

